---
import WorkDetail from '../../layouts/WorkDetail.astro';
---
<WorkDetail
  title="App Popular"
  company="Banco Popular Dominicano"
  period="2023 – Present"
  role="Tech Lead"
  category="Finance · iOS & Android"
  stack={["SwiftUI", "Kotlin", "iOS", "Android", "Agile", "CI/CD"]}
>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">Overview</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light mb-4">App Popular is Banco Popular Dominicano's flagship mobile app — one of the most widely used banking platforms in the Dominican Republic. The app gives clients full control of their finances from their phone, eliminating the need to visit a branch for everyday banking needs.</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light">Clients can check balances, move money, make every type of transaction and reclamation, and manage their account configurations — all through a secure, stable mobile experience on both iOS and Android.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">My Role</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light mb-4">As Tech Lead of an Agile team, I'm involved in the full software lifecycle of every feature we ship.</p>
    <div class="space-y-3 mt-4">
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Define and scope features based on product and business needs, producing technical documentation that minimizes risk before development begins.</p></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Design the data architecture required for each feature, aligned with client needs and backend capabilities.</p></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Participate in UX/UI decisions based on current backend structure, ensuring what gets designed can actually be built.</p></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Track features from conception through backend service readiness, with all security controls in place.</p></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Own deployment across Development, QA, and Production environments.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">Featured — Toke</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light">Toke is a payment infrastructure feature launched within App Popular to transform financial inclusion across the Dominican Republic. I contributed to the architecture design, security controls, and the full deployment pipeline that brought it to production.</p>
  </div>

</WorkDetail>